{"tid":2395623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★拜登：必須對抗及打敗 白人主義及本土主義！","createTime":"2021-02-05T04:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T08:21:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9e289eb2cbe5474a084edc9d40e9d14c9f1d1b","tid":2395623,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"美國總統拜登周四出席全國祈禱早餐會，指全國必須對抗及打敗政治極端主義、<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>白人至上主義及本土恐怖主義</strong></span>，又呼籲全國團結，尊重照顧其他人，又指國會遭暴力衝擊是攻擊美國的民主制度，威脅甚至奪去性命。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在眾議院國土安全委員會聽證會上，有專家警告，由右翼極端主義者煽動的本土威脅在可見的將來仍會是一大問題，又指國會被衝擊是白人至上主義行動的分水嶺，若當局不採取行動，這些行動不會消散。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/world/601c993934b03117433d5b1c/拜登籲團結對抗政治極端主義-共和黨議員支持極端陰謀論被解職\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F601c993934b03117433d5b1c%2F%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E7%B1%B2%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9-%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%A8%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF%E9%99%B0%E8%AC%80%E8%AB%96%E8%A2%AB%E8%A7%A3%E8%81%B7&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ERV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=a6eec13a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/world/601c993934b03117433d5b1c/拜登籲團結對抗政治極端主義-共和黨議員支持極端陰謀論被解職</a>"},{"pid":"ff15a9c3624f90d53fbfba9a369d73b257098eb8","tid":2395623,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5f7649150a640bc799c89019ab3b7a3dcc18ee","tid":2395623,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"